## Reset AGV Requirements

When `/atlas/reset_to_dock` is received by mission_node:

1. Log "RESET REQUESTED"
2. Cancel active mission
3. Stop robot (publish zero Twist)
4. Clear mission queue
5. Reset all internal state variables
6. Call Gazebo `/set_entity_state` to place robot at (0, 0, 0.01, yaw=90deg)
7. Set state to IDLE
8. Log "ROBOT RETURNED TO HOME"
9. Log "SYSTEM READY"

CLI alternative: `ros2 topic pub /atlas/reset_to_dock std_msgs/msg/Empty "{}" --once`

